{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"GS1 Composite configuration. Add to scanner configuration to scan GS1 Composite barcodes."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"(SBSDKBarcodeFormatGS1CompositeConfiguration) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatGS1CompositeConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When not enabled, the individual parts of GS1 Composite barcodes will be returned as separate items,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the respective formats are enabled (UPC-A, Code 128, MicroPDF417, PDF417)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Those barcode items will have their isGS1CompositePart field set to true."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If GS1 Composite scanning is enabled, the individual parts are never returned, even if their respective formats"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are enabled, except when the linear component is a UPC or EAN barcode. In that case the linear component might still"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"occasionally be returned as a separate result. If this situation needs to be avoided, remove the UPC and EAN formats from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the enabled formats."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If GS1 Composite scanning is disabled, but GS1 message validation is enabled, then the parts of the composite barcode may"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fail validation and be rejected."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/docume